    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for MRL 2. Validation metric V = 0.91 exceeds threshold. RH < 1.0 at worst-case operating point (RH = 0.94). CFD model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
